name: Forgiven Watchers of the Web
description: Having learned to work side-by-side with fruitsippers to achieve their goals, the Forgiven Watchers of the Web  owe a debt of gratitude to the Groodu for deliverance in their time of need. Now residing atop the oasis crabs of Kathoon, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
